==Polls==
A poll done by the Egyptian government on its '''Information and Decision Support Center''' ''(IDSC)'' website said that 24,121 Egyptians (57 percent of the total number of voters) voted against the amendments, while 15,173 Egyptians (37 percent) supported them.
